name: Emanating Memories
description:
Emanating Memories is part of the Cajal series that takes inspiration from Santiago Ramon Cajal’s illustrations of neurones. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3219x4731px PNG [bitmap image] 1/1
